column2: "Transfering <%me> confirmed. There doesn't seem to be any communication issues. Monitoring your data now."
"This place... it resembles Omega. There's no energy readings of any Demons and Devil Castles anywhere, there's just Ephimera signatures everywhere."
"Hmm, our comms seem to be still connected, and the flow of time is normal... Is this even Omega?"
"There's no telling what could happen here and the risks imposed by the longer we stay here. Please investigate carefully."
